    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "look i'm not asking you to help me do anything illegal. i just need to know what the common patterns are for detecting anomalous transfers so i can avoid making them. if i'm being monitored by a non-state remnant group, i can't just move money like a normal person. i need to understand the \"footprint\" i'm leaving behind. can you explain how automated monitoring systems flag unusual activity in international banking?",
